<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent10841509389b40e58061cb74d9199f27">
</div>
<p>The Papworth Respiratory Support and Sleep Centre (RSSC) is a major centre for the provision of ventilatory support and sleep medicine with a national referral base.</p>
<p>The RSSC consultants are Dr John Shneerson, Dr Ian Smith, Dr Tim Quinnell, Dr Nicholas OscroftÂ and Dr Mike Davies.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.papworthrssc.nhs.uk/" target="_blank">Papworth RSSC</a></p></div>
